text: Jacqueline Alison "Jackie" Martin (born 4 December 1971) is a road cyclist from South Africa. She represented her nation in the women's road race at the 1992 Summer Olympics and 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports-reference.com Category:South African female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of South Africa Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:1971 births
